Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class SignedPartition<K>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.SignedPartition<K>
public class SignedPartition<K>
extends java.lang.Object
Use this whenever you want to represent having N things with proportions that sum to 1, but where the weights are allowed to also be negative or > 1.

This is unlike a plain Partition, where the weights have to be a UnitFraction objects, i.e. in the interval [0, 1]).
